{"tid":1821800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国「母女共伺」遭踢爆做假","createTime":"2020-01-12T14:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T07:51:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1436cd14f967f2582dfbb1f27982983cd0fe48f3","tid":1821800,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0xd4cVuw1as82FKy.npj3g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTkxNi4yODQxNTMwMDU0NjQ1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/OnP4Pdx6usp6RyhOjJ8ayQ--~B/aD03ODY7dz01NDk7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/newtalk.tw/51009ace8f6944957d9b858e28c36b72\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F0xd4cVuw1as82FKy.npj3g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTkxNi4yODQxNTMwMDU0NjQ1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOnP4Pdx6usp6RyhOjJ8ayQ--~B%2FaD03ODY7dz01NDk7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewtalk.tw%2F51009ace8f6944957d9b858e28c36b72&h=43d8b72d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 圖：翻攝自微信<br />\n<br />\n中國網路近日瘋傳一張母女的照片，據了解，倆人一起從事特種行業，更主打「母女招牌」收費特別昂貴，令網友直呼不敢相信。後來被踢爆，倆人母女的身分是假的，原來是為了提高價格、賺錢的手段，有如愛情喜劇電影《千你奇緣》（Heartbreakers）的劇情。<br />\n<br />\n據傳，這對母女來自中國長沙，倆人身材姣好，母親體態維持良好，女兒也有清秀的臉龐。之所以轟動中國社群，是因為這對母女從事的是特種行業，讓許多網友不相信，質疑哪個母親會帶女兒做這種事，簡直毫無人倫，更遑論有沒有違法。<br />\n<br />\n但是網友曝光一張詢問價碼的對話紀錄，對方開出相當高的價錢；此外，客戶也可以檢查他們的身分證、戶口登記卡，讓許多網友信服這件事。根據這對母女的身分證及戶口登記卡，母親今年40歲，女兒竟然只有15歲。「長沙母女」立刻登上中國社群網站熱搜前幾名。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有眼尖的網友發現，這對母女的身分證、戶口登記卡根本是「假的」。網友分析，全國的戶口登記卡都是用專用的機器印出來的，通常是用點陣式印表機印出來的，字體大小、排版通常較整齊，且在「戶主關係欄」，幾乎不會再打一次名字，而母親的戶口登記卡卻不符上述要點。<br />\n<br />\n接著看到女兒戶口登記卡，不僅「戶主關係欄」填成性別，且證件照也不符規定，按照中國對證件照的要求，長髮雖然可以自然放下，但不能披頭散髮，女性一般會把頭髮綁起來，或是把頭髮披到後面，不會讓頭髮落在胸前。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zhjTwLApxmWwyWgxVBlTPg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/newtalk.tw/250210dd9dc298241262010a8a734330\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FzhjTwLApxmWwyWgxVBlTPg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewtalk.tw%2F250210dd9dc298241262010a8a734330&h=07bfe4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖：翻攝自微信<br />\n<br />\n由此看來，所謂的「母女共恃」完全徹頭徹尾的一場騙局，「你的眼睛業障重！」，其實是有心人士故意打造「母女」的組合，以收取更高的價格，這名闢謠的網友表示，這種手法屢見不鮮，仲介推出這種組合，不外乎是增加刺激度吸引顧客上門，再來就是可以提高價碼，該網友提醒民眾請勿上當。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/中國-母女共伺-遭踢爆做假-網友-眼睛業障重-104325424.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AF%8D%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%B1%E4%BC%BA-%E9%81%AD%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86%E5%81%9A%E5%81%87-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B-%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E6%A5%AD%E9%9A%9C%E9%87%8D-104325424.html&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=ca506dd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/中國-母女共伺-遭踢爆做假-網友-眼睛業障重-104325424.html</a>"},{"pid":"3dfacaa92fd0d6e18e49a37885c22ad9d93f4084","tid":1821800,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國人玩開未成年"},{"pid":"52885801709262573be0118fa110afee0676e8a8","tid":1821800,"uid":181655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"母女都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395e8f82d7b5fb7990e9ac1dd34f8242e56aeac7","tid":1821800,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T00:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00386daeaade443081823b6ee57e9af0d006f99","tid":1821800,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:00:38.000Z","msg":"唔係玩開幼稚園咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c324f6a0953838bf5d3badf32ed1da2042d0168","tid":1821800,"uid":64031,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:01:01.000